{"tid":723562,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［高鐵］最尾嗰個女演員演技好好","createTime":"2018-06-30T13:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T15:57:53.000Z","uid":24330,"like":13,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9f543f2c2ea3633f995582694a2b5870183f700c","tid":723562,"uid":24330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T13:30:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/212403_134d6cd5fcc8d9115aff2974bf817be7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F212403_134d6cd5fcc8d9115aff2974bf817be7.png&h=3a407ec5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢一個女演員完全為佢嘅角色增添左生命力<br />\n睇佢嘅眼神同表情完全演繹到<br />\n佢男朋友去咗武漢讀書之後食咗好多女<br />\n但重扮冇嘢，翻返嚟香港仲攬住佢<br />\n最慘嘅係佢男朋友而家返武漢食返餐<br />\n只係需要大半日時間果種無奈<br />\n佢呢一個笑容我真係睇到好傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw佢叫咩名？"},{"pid":"dde7ba5285592f009dfebbfca873275d38db7caf","tid":723562,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T13:31:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd4da2f9c6bef187934da3cbcbbcf5e6fb38a52","tid":723562,"uid":120715,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T13:32:52.000Z","msg":"條女話以前北上食女要幾日先返屋企<br />\n依家終於日日食完都返到屋企啦"},{"pid":"2f66c0dfc8ca0352439ccd235e7a001620bb54e8","tid":723562,"uid":24330,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T13:39:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/213257_4440f15c004f3809aa72cc6e464567be.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F213257_4440f15c004f3809aa72cc6e464567be.png&h=9d09ebaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢一個老細同秘書佢哋嘅背影都好悲傷<br />\n因為佢哋見完個香港客仲要車佢去廣州南站<br />\n一來一回可能見兩個幾鐘<br />\n個香港客個半鐘已經返到屋企食飯<br />\n但係佢哋個幾鐘後可能仲要返公司<br />\n執埋D手尾先返到屋企<br />\n個女秘書笑嘅表情都硬晒<br />\n我諗佢返到公司都無心情同老細執手尾<br />\n兩個嘅演技都好好"},{"pid":"96b44be7cede31f9bec3a353dfd71d9305483d43","tid":723562,"uid":24330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dde7ba5285592f009dfebbfca873275d38db7caf","tid":723562,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T13:31:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T13:42:41.000Z","msg":"又放伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a237b273c4c995c7bcb48dfccd524187613b4970","tid":723562,"uid":24330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcd4da2f9c6bef187934da3cbcbbcf5e6fb38a52","tid":723562,"uid":120715,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T13:32:52.000Z","msg":"條女話以前北上食女要幾日先返屋企<br />\n依家終於日日食完都返到屋企啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T13:43:37.000Z","msg":"得條毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa51130a075883ff811cfe2b074a59bab14c06c","tid":723562,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a237b273c4c995c7bcb48dfccd524187613b4970","tid":723562,"uid":24330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcd4da2f9c6bef187934da3cbcbbcf5e6fb38a52","tid":723562,"uid":120715,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T13:32:52.000Z","msg":"條女話以前北上食女要幾日先返屋企<br />\n依家終於日日食完都返到屋企啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T13:43:37.000Z","msg":"得條毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T13:44:20.000Z","msg":"哈哈<br />\n被你發現左添"},{"pid":"b1b892920399f13da69b714f0f80675aaf32365a","tid":723562,"uid":24330,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T13:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/214455_db2bfd625e2b9cdd693bea27db5f74c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F214455_db2bfd625e2b9cdd693bea27db5f74c4.png&h=d294b2ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你以為佢同香港個老婆講？<br />\n其實佢同虎門住嗰個二奶講<br />\n佢喺廣州南站搭兩個站就到虎門<br />\n食完飯再食二奶<br />\n食完返屋企再食老婆<br />\n一日三餐好和味<br />\n如果唔係點會笑得咁淫？<br />\n所以佢演技都好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9377b654a899903af28ea7fb1224bed6ee5d02","tid":723562,"uid":46500,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b1b892920399f13da69b714f0f80675aaf32365a","tid":723562,"uid":24330,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T13:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/214455_db2bfd625e2b9cdd693bea27db5f74c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F214455_db2bfd625e2b9cdd693bea27db5f74c4.png&h=d294b2ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你以為佢同香港個老婆講？<br />\n其實佢同虎門住嗰個二奶講<br />\n佢喺廣州南站搭兩個站就到虎門<br />\n食完飯再食二奶<br />\n食完返屋企再食老婆<br />\n一日三餐好和味<br />\n如果唔係點會笑得咁淫？<br />\n所以佢演技都好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T13:52:24.000Z","msg":"根本成條片充斥詐騙成份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d64c6cf0bbcd7e29fcbf41d493edd272509246c9","tid":723562,"uid":24330,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T14:09:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/215755_2c5a88d478368fe82cbcd73fb8137929.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F215755_2c5a88d478368fe82cbcd73fb8137929.png&h=e00b1fee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n知唔知點解個阿婆會沖出嚟？<br />\n因為佢哋好耐冇返去<br />\n長假期永遠都搶唔到飛<br />\n以前阿婆個啲親戚朝頭早話出門返去<br />\n過關去深圳搭飛機中午就返到<br />\n依家搞到差唔多太陽落山先返到去<br />\n來回加埋起嚟唔見咗一日<br />\n仲要未計搶飛可能時間更少<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/215754_df002b4c6bd6fc36a75e2e5a306e45ec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F215754_df002b4c6bd6fc36a75e2e5a306e45ec.png&h=c8c1d93b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解個男人咁嘅表情<br />\n唔係因為佢加埋坐咗咁耐車<br />\n而係佢肉赤每人貴咗兩三百蚊唔坐飛機<br />\n仲要浪費左時間等車<br />\n仲要係廣州南站同埋高鐵上面都完全冇啖好食<br />\n佢好懷念飛機餐先會咁樣"},{"pid":"8a935b3299f1953295791f22892d647d48175de2","tid":723562,"uid":164050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T14:12:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0642a2952aced8bc89bcf4d5234776a6dab82a7","tid":723562,"uid":24330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T14:25:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/221424_01eda85dbacedee5f521f1c18a245ba5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F221424_01eda85dbacedee5f521f1c18a245ba5.png&h=07e3e371&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢一個廣告演技最差係佢哋啦<br />\n高鐵去桂林<br />\n到底去陽朔落車定桂林北落車定桂林西落車<br />\n幾個人一齊去一定嘈到好金<br />\n一定唔會咁開心嘅樣<br />\n去到桂林再去揾唔同景點嘅交通又會嘈多一獲金"},{"pid":"8702c4d0e1ecf3c775a8b03bef41ee2bcaaba4cb","tid":723562,"uid":24330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T14:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/222900_9056ef95bf26b9a08dc63fd0d5055321.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F222900_9056ef95bf26b9a08dc63fd0d5055321.png&h=66ddf551&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/222901_9056ef95bf26b9a08dc63fd0d5055321.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F222901_9056ef95bf26b9a08dc63fd0d5055321.png&h=8eca65f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後我用高鐵式英文祝大家旅途愉快<br />\nLV TU YU KUAI"},{"pid":"8192e76306449f9a7d7d6c67f2868ae52d8aebd7","tid":723562,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T15:00:49